{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"result","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/result","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p>属性<code>result</code>定义了滤镜的分配名。如果提供了它，则经过滤镜处理的结果即图形可以再次滤镜处理，在后继滤镜（即另一个<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code></a>元素）上通过一个<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/in\">in</a></code>属性引用之前的结果。如果没有提供<code>result</code>值，而且如果下一个滤镜也没有提供<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/in\">in</a></code>属性值，则输出只可作为下一个滤镜的隐式输入。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>无</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td>&lt;filter-primitive-reference&gt;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可变性</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/filters.html#FilterPrimitiveResultAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>注意<code>&lt;filter-primitive-reference&gt;</code>不是一个 XML ID，换句话说，<code>&lt;filter-primitive-reference&gt;</code>只在给定的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code></a>元素内部有意义，因此只有局部范围。在同一个<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code></a>元素内部，同一个<code>&lt;filter-primitive-reference&gt;</code>出现多次也是合法的。如果引用了，<code>&lt;filter-primitive-reference&gt;</code>将使用在给定结果前面、离给定结果最近的滤镜。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列元素可以使用<code>result</code>属性：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#filterprimitive\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#FilterPrimitive\">滤镜元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"result","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/result","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/result/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/result","title":"result"}],"pageTitle":"result - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}